  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK705">
<l>kuṟippiṟ kuṟippuṇarā vāyi ṉuṟuppiṉu</l>
<l>ḷeṉṉa payattavō kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of what use are the eyes amongst one's members, if they cannot by their own indications dive those of another ?.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
